{{Infobox Magazine | title = Forza Milan! | image_file = | image_size = | image_alt = | image_caption = | editor = | editor_title = | previous_editor = | staff_writer = | frequency = Monthly | circulation = | category = [[Association Football|Football]] | company = [[Panini Group|Panini]] | publisher = | firstdate = {{Start date|1968}} | finaldate = {{End date|2018}} | country = Italy | based = [[Milan]], [[Lombardy]] | language = [[Italian language|Italian]] | website = [http://www.forzamilanonline.com/ ForzaMilanOnLine.com] | issn = 1122-8059 }}
'''''Forza Milan!''''' was a monthly Italian sports [[magazine]] entirely dedicated to the [[association football|football]] [[Club (organization)|club]] [[A.C. Milan]]. It featured articles, posters and photos of AC Milan players including both the first team players and the youth system kids, as well as club employees. It also featured anecdotes and famous episodes from the club's history.
